sections.name: Launch Agent 6
sections.content: The documents herein specify all of the logic for Launch Agent 6, including Launch Agent 6's strategy and how it uses the Sky Primitives to operationalize this strategy.

agent_scope_database.name: Introduction
agent_scope_database.content:
Launch Agent 6 is an Agent focused on building credit infrastructure for permissionless finance, with a focus on the Plasma ecosystem. Launch Agent 6 serves as a neutral platform enabling stablecoin distribution hubs—including exchanges, wallets, and neobanks—to access institutional-grade lending infrastructure underpinning USDS, sUSDS and other Sky benefits.

With a focus on USDT, Launch Agent 6 acts as the central liquidity hub catalyzing the expansion of USDT-denominated assets across DeFi and OTC lending markets, RWAs, and PayFi within Sky's collateral portfolio. Launch Agent 6 provides USDT holders with access to the Sky Savings Rate within its own suite of B2B2C and B2C savings products.

agent_scope_database.name: Governance Information Unrelated To Root Edit Primitive

agent_scope_database.name: Sky Forum
agent_scope_database.content: Launch Agent 6 uses the Sky Forum for governance-related discussion. Posts should use the 'Launch Agent 6 Prime' category.

agent_scope_database.name: Sky Ecosystem Emergency Response
agent_scope_database.content: The documents herein specify Launch Agent 6's emergency response protocol in situations that impact the entire Sky Ecosystem. This protocol will be specified in a future iteration of the Launch Agent 6 Artifact.

agent_scope_database.name: Agent-Specific Emergency Response
agent_scope_database.content: The documents herein specify Launch Agent 6's emergency response protocol in situations solely impacting Launch Agent 6 versus the broader Sky Ecosystem. This protocol will be specified in a future iteration of the Launch Agent 6 Artifact.
